name: Diamond Swallows
description:
These grey, black, and pink Swallow charms measure approx 2x1 inches. They are met in the middle with a silver diamond charm.

Secured with a silver chain, standard 16 inches. Charms are made from hard cut plastic and sealed for protection.


*The Swallow has been said to symbolize a safe return home. When a sailor saw a swallow at sea, he knew he was very near land, and the swallows would lead them home. It is said that if the sailor does not survive his travels, and ends up drowning, the birds alight upon his soul and carry him from the murky waters, up to heaven.
